DATA : PA_D_01 TYPE P DECIMALS 4,
       PA_D_02 TYPE P DECIMALS 10.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OFBLOCK B1 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-000.
    SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
        SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT1(50) FD_LABEL.
    SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

    PARAMETERS : PA_D_RAW TYPE P DECIMALS 11.

    PA_D_01=TRUNC(PA_D_RAW*10000)/10000.
    PA_D_02=TRUNC(PA_D_RAW*10000000000)/10000000000.

    WRITE : PA_D_01 DECIMALS 4,
            /PA_D_02 DECIMALS 10.
SELECTION-SCREEN : END OF BLOCK B1.

AT SELECTION-SCREEN OUTPUT.
